      • readADInterfaceMCCObjects

        public static java.util.ArrayList<ADInterfaceMCCObjectType> readADInterfaceMCCObjects(java.lang.String s)
                                                                               throws java.io.FileNotFoundException,
                                                                                      javax.xml.parsers.ParserConfigurationException,
                                                                                      org.xml.sax.SAXException,
                                                                                      java.io.IOException
        Read adInterfaceMCC object types from the xml configuration..
        Parameters:
        s - xml configuation file path.
        Returns:
        ArrayList containing elements of ADInterfaceMCC Device.
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - if configuration file can't be found.
        javax.xml.parsers.ParserConfigurationException - if configuration file couldn't be read properly.
        org.xml.sax.SAXException - if error occurs while configuration file is parsed.
        java.io.IOException - if I/O error occurs while parsing configuration file.
